I walk through how to make kits for Football Manager 2015 and then how to import them into the game. This process works for logos as well.

Apologies for the mic quality during the first part of this video, it was a nightmare trying to make this work.

Template can be found here: http://sortitoutsi.net/forums/topic/177/ss09-13-template-thread

